Package model.projectile

Class EnemyProjectile

java.lang.Object
model.GameObject
model.DynamicObject
model.projectile.Projectile
model.projectile.EnemyProjectile
public class EnemyProjectile extends Projectile
The EnemyProjectile class handles the specificities with the projectile being shot from a shootEnemy or the boss.
It also can only hurt a hero.
